\section{Defining the Language}

In order to make sense of user input, we need to define a \gls{grammar}.

<<lispy.mpc>>=
integer  : /-?[0-9]+/ ;
decimal  : /-?[0-9]+\.[0-9]+/ ;
number   : <decimal> | <integer> ;
operator : '+' | '-' | '*' | '/' | '%' | '^';
expr     : <number> | '(' <operator> <expr>+ ')' ;
lispy    : /^/ <operator> <expr>+ /$/ ;
@

\todoo{Describe this trick}
